---
---

<section id="community" class="section-padding bg-cream-100 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute -left-32 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-sage-200 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="reveal space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-card">
              <img src="/images/office/hero-2.jpg" alt="Montezuma community" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-card">
              <img src="/images/office/gallery-2.jpg" alt="Local families at Montezuma Dental" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 pt-8 space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-card">
              <img src="/images/office/gallery-3.jpg" alt="Montezuma Dental office" class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="bg-sage-500 rounded-3xl p-6 text-white">
              <p class="font-display text-2xl mb-2">Proudly Montezuma</p>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">Deep roots in our community since day one.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <p class="reveal section-label mb-4">Community Connection</p>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 section-title text-balance mb-6">
          More Than a Clinic.<br />A Community Partner.
        </h2>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-charcoal-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Montezuma Dental isn't just located in Montezuma—we're part of it. We know your neighbors, cheer at local events, and treat every patient like family because many of them are.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3 text-charcoal-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
          When you choose us, you're choosing a practice that invests in this community's health, happiness, and future. That's a promise no corporate chain can make.
        </p>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {
            ['Local Families', 'Hometown Values', 'Generations of Trust', 'Iowa Hospitality'].map((tag) => (
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-sage-600 shadow-soft border border-cream-200">
                {tag}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
